title: Go documentation: Typo in Effective Go - Methods - Pointers vs. Values
body:
by **joseph.macfarlane**: 
Steps to reproduce:
1. Visit http://golang.org/doc/effective_go.html#pointers_vs_values
2. Scroll to Methods - Pointers vs. Values
3. review third snippet

Expected:
No unmatched brackets

Actual:
line 5: 	return len(data), nil)
